&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experienced in media agency 1 year above&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High levels of energy and a desire to deliver great work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A willingness to learn and desire to challenge yourself&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Best in class attention to detail and accuracy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A collaborative approach&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A team player attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A willingness to go above and beyond&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for the media industry and specifically the importance of investment in the process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
