&lt;li&gt;Ensure projects/campaigns are tracked and measured based on agreed KPIs and media efficiencies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To be a team player and work well with all members of the team to ensure all tasks are fulfilled. Guide and advise the wider team on best practices, innovation, and work processes.&lt;/li&gt;
